air mic’ MacNeil 42 und seine Mutter Katherine Somerled 32. Er hatte mit Beatrice Somerled mindestens 2 Söhne und 1 Tochter. Er starb 1235 im Alter von 54 Jahren in Schottland, United Kingdom und wurde in Scotland begraben."},"ht":{"1181–1235":"1181–1235","–1235":"–1235","–Male":"Desede","1185–1240":"1185–1240","1230–Female":"1230–Desede","1235–1293":"1235–1293","1140–1191":"1140–1191","1150–Female":"1150–Desede","Abt 1230":"about 1230","1235":"1235","before 1179":"before 1179","1230":"1230","1240":"1240","1185":"1185","Abt 1235":"about 1235","1140":"1140","1150":"1150","1293":"1293","1181":"1181","1191":"1191","Ardlamont, Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Ecosse, United Kingdom","Lamont, Lochow, Argyllshire, Scotland":"Lamont, Argyll, Ecosse, United Kingdom","Lamont, Cowal Peninsula, Argyllshire, Scotland.":"Lamont, Argyll, Ecosse, United Kingdom","Scotland":"Scotland","Glassary, Argyll, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Glassary, Argyll, Ecosse, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1181–1235":"1181–1235","–1235":"–1235","–Male":"elhunyt","1185–1240":"1185–1240","1230–Female":"1230–elhunyt","1235–1293":"1235–1293","1140–1191":"1140–1191","1150–Female":"1150–elhunyt","Abt 1230":"1230 körül","1235":"1235","before 1179":"1179 előtt","1230":"1230","1240":"1240","1185":"1185","Abt 1235":"1235 körül","1140":"1140","1150":"1150","1293":"1293","1181":"1181","1191":"1191","Ardlamont, Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Skócia, United Kingdom","Lamont, Lochow, Argyllshire, Scotland":"Lamont, Argyll, Skócia, United Kingdom","Lamont, Cowal Peninsula, Argyllshire, Scotland.":"Lamont, Argyll, Skócia, United Kingdom","Scotland":"Scotland","Glassary, Argyll, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Glassary, Argyll, Skócia, United Kingdom"},"id":{"1181–1235":"1181–1235","–1235":"–1235","–Male":"TelahMeninggal","1185–1240":"1185–1240","1230–Female":"1230–Telah Meninggal","1235–1293":"1235–1293","1140–1191":"1140–1191","1150–Female":"1150–Telah Meninggal","